<h3 class="wiki-nav-item pb-2" id="userdata">
    What is convert_to_portable.bat?
</h3>
<div class="ms-3">
    <p>
        This file moves OpenTabletDriver's settings to a folder called <i>userdata</i> next to OpenTabletDriver itself
        rather than being stored in <i>%localappdata%\OpenTabletDriver</i>. This allows OpenTabletDriver to be completely portable,
        all in one folder.
    </p>
</div>

